title: Lunchbox Tries to Get Free Things As A 'Social Media Influencer' + Bleeped Lyrics Game: Name the State
itunes:title: Lunchbox Tries to Get Free Things As A 'Social Media Influencer' + Bleeped Lyrics Game: Name the State
description:
Lunchbox calls businesses and tells them he has tons of followers on Instagram to try and get things for free. We play a game where you have to guess the name of the State bleeped out of song lyrics.
